item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: romantic-panini
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:

Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)

...or something like this:

The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.

As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

item.title: Refund and Returns Policy
item.dc:creator: romantic-panini
item.content:encoded:
This is a sample page.

Overview

Our refund and returns policy lasts 30 days. If 30 days have passed since your purchase, we cant offer you a full refund or exchange.

To be eligible for a return, your item must be unused and in the same condition that you received it. It must also be in the original packaging.

Several types of goods are exempt from being returned. Perishable goods such as food, flowers, newspapers or magazines cannot be returned. We also do not accept products that are intimate or sanitary goods, hazardous materials, or flammable liquids or gases.

Additional non-returnable items:

  • Gift cards
  • Downloadable software products
  • Some health and personal care items

To complete your return, we require a receipt or proof of purchase.

Please do not send your purchase back to the manufacturer.

There are certain situations where only partial refunds are granted:

  • Book with obvious signs of use
  • CD, DVD, VHS tape, software, video game, cassette tape, or vinyl record that has been opened.
  • Any item not in its original condition, is damaged or missing parts for reasons not due to our error.
  • Any item that is returned more than 30 days after delivery

Refunds

Once your return is received and inspected, we will send you an email to notify you that we have received your returned item. We will also notify you of the approval or rejection of your refund.

If you are approved, then your refund will be processed, and a credit will automatically be applied to your credit card or original method of payment, within a certain amount of days.

Late or missing refunds

If you havent received a refund yet, first check your bank account again.

Then contact your credit card company, it may take some time before your refund is officially posted.

Next contact your bank. There is often some processing time before a refund is posted.

If youve done all of this and you still have not received your refund yet, please contact us at {email address}.

Sale items

Only regular priced items may be refunded. Sale items cannot be refunded.

Exchanges

We only replace items if they are defective or damaged. If you need to exchange it for the same item, send us an email at {email address} and send your item to: {physical address}.

Gifts

If the item was marked as a gift when purchased and shipped directly to you, youll receive a gift credit for the value of your return. Once the returned item is received, a gift certificate will be mailed to you.

If the item wasnt marked as a gift when purchased, or the gift giver had the order shipped to themselves to give to you later, we will send a refund to the gift giver and they will find out about your return.

Shipping returns

To return your product, you should mail your product to: {physical address}.

You will be responsible for paying for your own shipping costs for returning your item. Shipping costs are non-refundable. If you receive a refund, the cost of return shipping will be deducted from your refund.

Depending on where you live, the time it may take for your exchanged product to reach you may vary.

If you are returning more expensive items, you may consider using a trackable shipping service or purchasing shipping insurance. We dont guarantee that we will receive your returned item.

Need help?

Contact us at {email} for questions related to refunds and returns.

item.title: Mima Xari 4G Complete Stroller with Car Seat Adapters
item.dc:creator: romantic-panini
item.content:encoded:
The only stroller made with leatherette fabric, the Mima Xari 4G stroller is more than a pretty face. With a chic design and advanced features, this highly-customizable stroller strikes the perfect balance of fashion and functionality.
The Mima Xari frame can be used with either a stroller seat or a carrycot/bassinetand can change between the two in less than 15 seconds. Thanks to Mima's patented design, the carrycot is cleverly zipped into the seat itself. With the use of adapters, the Xari is also compatible with a number of infant car seats. To ensure the most comfortable ride, the Mima Xari features three recline positions and a seat that can face toward you or the world.
Choose from many color combinations for your Mima Xari stroller, which includes the stroller frame, seat box with carry cot zipped inside, and matching seat pad and carry cot textiles. The Xari 4G stroller includes car seat adapters for attaching a Maxi-Cosi, Cybex, Nuna, or Clek infant car seat.
Patented "carry cot inside" system allows for carry cot to be stored within seat when not in use
Compatible with infant car seats (Maxi Cosi / Nuna / Cybex / Clek adapters included, UPPAbaby Mesa adapter sold separately)
Leatherette fabric is easily cleanable, resistant and breathable
Three-position adjustable handlebar
Seat pad with a 5-point safety harness
Highly-resistant wheels, with sports shoe technology so they never deflate
Front wheels with 360 swivel and wheel lock
Three seat recline angles
Two storage baskets with magnetic lids keep items out of sight
Folds compactly with seat attached with the press of a button and lift of a lever
Rear brake

item.title: Nuna MIXX Next and PIPA Lite R Travel System
item.dc:creator: romantic-panini
item.content:encoded:
The next generation of Nunas most popular stroller features a smaller fold, a smoother ride and a new name: the Nuna MIXX Next.
The MIXX Next builds on the MIXX by folding 6.5 inches smaller than its predecessor and standing on its own when folded. It also offers better maneuverability, thanks to improved suspension and redesigned rubber wheels, and has a magnetic buckle that makes it easier to harness your child.
The MIXX Next includes Nuna's unique ring-shaped car seat adapter, which allows parents to attach and detach a Nuna car seat with one hand. The stroller also pairs with the MIXX Series Bassinet, which is approved safe for overnight sleeping. Reverse the seat to face you or face forward, and recline the seat to a flat position that's safe for newborns.
The Nuna PIPA Lite R combines the safety and 5.3-pound weight of the PIPA Lite infant car seat with the greater adjustability of Nuna's new RELX base. Pronounced like "relax," the RELX base offers four recline positions and solves common installation problems, allowing you to customize the fit of your car seat for both your baby and your vehicle.
The PIPA Lite R does not include the Sky Drape magnetic cover and cannot be installed without the base for taxis or travel. See our Nuna PIPA comparison to learn about the differences between Nuna's five infant car seats.
This travel system includes a Nuna PIPA Lite R infant car seat, a RELX car seat base and the MIXX ring adapter.
MIXX Next Stroller
Folds to a length that's 6.5" shorter than the original MIXX and stands when folded
Rubber wheels offer enhanced all-wheel suspension for superior maneuverability on rough terrain
Can be used as a travel system with Nuna infant car seats (with included ring adapter)
Pairs with Nuna MIXX Series Bassinet, which is safe for overnight sleeping
Magnetic buckle makes it quick and easy to buckle your child
Front wheels swivel for maneuverability or lock for stability
Compact fold, no matter what position the seat is facing
Front and rear-wheel progressive suspension absorbs shock for a smooth ride
One-hand, five-position recline, including to true flat sleeping position
Hand-sewn, leather-look handlebar and belly bar
Stylish accents, including a dark matte frame and chrome-accented wheels
Premium cotton fabric
Adjustable handlebar and leg support
Oversized, UPF 50+ canopy with extendable eyeshade, mesh ventilation panels and underside double-quilted stitch work
Removable, rotating arm bar fits kids of various sizes
Large storage basket includes compartment divider
Trolley function makes stroller easy to carry when not in use
PIPA Lite R Infant Car Seat
At 5.3 pounds, the Nuna PIPA Lite R is the lightest infant car seat on the market
Made with aerospace aluminum, along with lightweight Aeroflex foam that can absorb and diffuse energy away from baby in a crash
Load leg in steel-reinforced base attaches to floor of car to reduce rotation during impact by up to 90 percent, with crumple zone that absorbs impact and minimizes force to baby
Rigid (metal) LATCH connectors on base are 50 percent stronger than a typical belt LATCH
Flame-resistant materials contain no added fire retardant chemicals
Side-impact protection
Patented memory foam headrest provides custom support as baby grows
Two-step, five-second install, with indicators that turn green to signal a correct installation
Made of comfortable micro-knit fabric, with a removable organic cotton infant insert
Removable UPF 50+ canopy with flip-out eyeshade
Compatible with strollers from Nuna and many other brands
Integrated harness holders help you buckle in baby with ease
Leather-look carry handle adds luxury and comfort
FAA-certified for airplanes with base
Crumple zone within the steel load leg minimizes forward rotation by up to 90%, absorbing impact and minimizes force transferred to baby
Reclines to four positions, with two positions for babies 4-20 pounds and two positions for 21-32 pounds, to add comfort as your child grows
Recline button confirms safe riding angles without the need for bubble levels
4-position rigid LATCH connectors reduce the gap between your vehicle seat and base, creating a more secure installation and fitting more vehicle models
Color-coded installation indicators confirm correct connections to the vehicle
Anti rebound panel reduces rearward motion and ensures a flush fit against your vehicle seat
Locking 3 piece steel stability leg has a wide range of adjustment to fit most vehicles including middle seat jumps

item.title: 2022 Bumbleride Era Stroller
item.dc:creator: romantic-panini
item.content:encoded:
Bumbleride brings its eco-conscious, adventure-ready style to the Bumbleride Era, the company's first stroller with four wheels and a reversible seat that allows your child to face you or face forward.
New for 2022, an updated brake is easier to use and sandal friendly, while the bumper bar is also easier to attach and remove. Several new color options are available, including Sand beige with a checked print contrast, Dusk grey with a wool blend fabric that is soft to the touch, and Olive green with a matte black frame.
While the Era isn't intended for jogging, it still conquers rough terrain with its tough, air-filled tires and all-wheel suspension. With its compact, standing fold and smaller footprint, the Bumbleride Era is the perfect companion for families who want a rugged all-terrain stroller that's still convenient for everyday life.
The Bumbleride Era is newborn-ready when you recline the seat to a flat position or pair the stroller with an infant car seat or overnight-approved bassinet. Easy-access pockets and a generous cargo basket store everything you need for the day.
The fabrics on Bumbleride strollers are water-resistant, thanks to PFC-free durable water repellant, and plastic components are made from 25% recycled recycled fishing nets. Plus, the Era is the first stroller to feature a handlebar made of corkan all-natural material that's durable, antimicrobial, comfortable, non-toxic and sustainable.

item.title: Nuna MIXX Next Stroller
item.dc:creator: romantic-panini
item.content:encoded:
The next generation of Nunas most popular stroller features a smaller fold, a smoother ride and a new name: the Nuna MIXX Next.
The MIXX Next builds on the MIXX by folding 6.5 inches smaller than its predecessor and standing on its own when folded. It also offers better maneuverability, thanks to improved suspension and redesigned rubber wheels, and has a magnetic buckle that makes it easier to harness your child.
The MIXX Next comes with Nuna's unique ring-shaped car seat adapter and is compatible with all Nuna infant car seats. The ring adapter allows parents to attach and detach the car seat with one hand, making it a snap to move baby from car to stroller. The stroller also pairs with the MIXX Series Bassinet, which is approved safe for overnight sleeping.
Rugged rubber tires with enhanced all-wheel suspension make for smooth strolling over any type of terrain, while premium fabrics with leatherette details create a stroller that's as stylish as it is practical.
The MIXX Next features an all-season seat that helps keep your child cool in warm weather. The reversible, two-piece bamboo seat insert helps wick moisture and can be removed to reveal an all-mesh seat back. A no-rethread harness makes for easy adjustments as your child grows.
The Nuna MIXX Next stands when folded, locks automatically and can be trolleyed for easy transport. The stroller features five comfortable positions: Reverse the seat to face you or face forward, or recline the seat completely so baby can nap in comfort.

item.title: 2022 Bumbleride Speed Jogging Stroller
item.dc:creator: romantic-panini
item.content:encoded:
As Bumbleride's performance jogging stroller, the Bumbleride Speed offers three front wheel settings for walking, jogging and training. Lock the front wheel for long-distance running, keep it swiveling 360 degrees for city walking, or engage a partial lock with a 20-degree swivel for light jogging and all-terrain trails.
New for 2022, an updated brake is easier to use and sandal friendly, while the bumper bar is also easier to attach and remove. One new color option has been added to the Speed, Supernova with Maritime blue color-blocked with Clay and Sea Glass accents.
With its 3-year warranty and range of use from birth to 65 pounds, the Bumbleride Speed is built to last. The stroller is compatible with numerous infant car seat brands to create a travel system and can also be paired with a bassinet (sold separately) that keeps infants cozy.
Plus, the Bumbleride Speed is one of the most eco-friendly strollers on the planet. Bumbleride uses 28 recycled water bottles per stroller to create the 100% recycled polyester fabrics used for most colors, as well as an innovative solution dye process that uses 89% percent less water.
Bumbleride strollers are free of fire retardants, PVC, phthalate and other chemicals. Fabrics are water-resistant, thanks to PFC-free durable water repellant, and plastic components are made from 25% recycled recycled fishing nets.

The Bumbleride Indie may be the only stroller you ever need, thanks to its 3-year warranty and range of use from birth to 55 pounds. item.title: Veer Cruiser All-Terrain Wagon with Canopy and Sidewalls
item.dc:creator: romantic-panini
item.content:encoded:
The Veer Cruiser combines the functionality of a premium stroller with the classic fun of a wagon: Whether you push it ahead or pull it behind you, the Veer is a versatile companion for all your family adventures.
With its rugged tires and front-wheel suspension, the Veer can tackle any terrain on your next trip to the beach or the woods. Yet despite its sturdiness and passenger weight capacity of 110 pounds, the Veer weighs as much as a typical double stroller, thanks to its lightweight, aircraft-grade aluminum construction. The Veer folds flat and stands when folded for easy storage.
Accessories sold separately add even more function to the Veer: Add car seat adapters to create a travel system, canopies for sun protection, sidewalls for a pop of color, a storage basket large enough to hold a cooler, and more.
The Veer Cruiser comes equipped with two foldable seats with 3-point harnesses, two cup holders and a removable snack/drink tray. This listing includes the Veer Cruiser wagon, along with one canopy and the sidewall kit.

item.title: Cybex Mios3 Stroller - Spring Blossom
item.dc:creator: romantic-panini
item.content:encoded:
Cybex's latest fashion collection is in full bloom: The Spring Blossom version of the Mios3 stroller is whimsical and vibrant, with embroidered floral appliqus, jeweled adornments and a red striped ribbon accent.
With its modern, minimalistic design and unique mesh features, the Cybex Mios3 brings a sense of airiness to a compact stroller ideal for exploring the city.
The seat and footrest of the Cybex Mios3 is constructed of breathable mesh that keeps your child comfortable in warm temperatures (just add the seat inlay for extra comfort and warmth in other seasons).
The Mios3 weighs less than 20 pounds and spans less than 20 inches in width, making it nimble in tight city spaces. But with its aluminum frame, all-wheel suspension and 55-pound weight capacity, the Mios provides the durability and maneuverability of a larger stroller. Fold the Mios with just one hand into a self-standing position that makes it easy to grab and go.
Use your stroller from birth by adding the Spring Blossom editions of the Cloud Q car seat or the Mios Lux Carrycot.
